data.text: @Rachel_Mantell Yup! Another reasons I'm a strong believer in submitting to the systematic unfolding of aggregated statistics when it comes to public health...
@Rachel_Mantell That's the one! Very sore arm too. Pretty much all better now. Second one booked for July. Feels slightly unreal, in the best possible sense.
@chrisbaraniuk AZ, yes. Didn't know what I was getting until I turned up. Certainly nothing major or to moan about. Very stiff arm, mild flu-like feelings. The smallest of small prices to pay!
@TomChatfield AZ? I had a raised temperature, bit of arm soreness but really nothing major at all so I seem to have got away without too much trouble! Really does seem to vary for people.
